00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:02.340
Welcome to functional safety.

00:00:02.340 --> 00:00:08.540
In this module, you'll learn how to analyze and design automotive systems to reduce risk.

00:00:08.540 --> 00:00:11.416
Three functional safety experts from Elektrobit,

00:00:11.416 --> 00:00:14.940
Dheeraj, Stephanie, and Benjamin will be leading the module.

00:00:14.940 --> 00:00:20.460
Within the module, you'll use the framework provided by ISO 26262,

00:00:20.460 --> 00:00:23.595
the international standard on functional safety.

00:00:23.595 --> 00:00:28.680
Functional safety is an important part of designing autonomous vehicles and it's often

00:00:28.680 --> 00:00:34.004
a difficult skill set to acquire because it is so specific to the automotive industry.

00:00:34.004 --> 00:00:37.785
We're excited for you to learn these skills and we hope that, eventually,

00:00:37.785 --> 00:00:40.500
you'll have the opportunity to apply them in designing

00:00:40.500 --> 00:00:43.865
safe, functional, self-driving cars.

00:00:43.865 --> 00:00:46.020
Hi, my name is Stephanie Hollyer.

00:00:46.020 --> 00:00:50.340
