00:00:55.050 --> 00:00:56.880
And I'm Benjamin Brentrop.

00:00:56.880 --> 00:01:00.145
I'm a functional safety manager at Elektrobit in Germany.

00:01:00.145 --> 00:01:03.315
My background is in automotive system software development.

00:01:03.315 --> 00:01:04.780
For the past six years,

00:01:04.780 --> 00:01:08.130
I've worked in the area of functional safety for instrument clusters,

00:01:08.130 --> 00:01:11.765
transmission control, avick controls and body control units.

00:01:11.765 --> 00:01:14.040
Hi my name is Deeraj Sharma.

00:01:14.040 --> 00:01:16.467
